|5 |     TABLE SCAN   |INNR(idx1)    |5        |338 |
|6 |    TABLE SCAN    |OUTR          |990      |945 |
|7 |   TABLE SCAN     |OUTR2(idx3)   |334      |97  |
=====================================================

